  "caveats": [
    "Primary comparison uses Ray driver SWEPRO_AGENT_TRACE timestamps grouped by trace_replay_source_trajectory_id; this gives a paired comparison over the same 160 source trajectories.",
    "KV Tachometer collection was manually stopped after the Ray job because the old launcher terminal-state grep missed Ray's 'Job ... succeeded' wording; counter rates over collector wall time are therefore not used as primary evidence.",
    "Frontend pod logs are cumulative across frontend restarts, so routing-mode evidence must be read from the relevant startup tail: KV run has kv-events subscriber; approx run logs 'Skipping KV event subscription (use_kv_events=false, overlap_score_credit=1)'.",
    "Approx engines were relaunched with SWEPRO_DYNAMO_ROUTER_KV_EVENTS=0, so the approximate run disables engine KV event publication as well as frontend KV event consumption."
